item.title: Self Reliance Devotional
item.description: Members (and friends) can choose from five different groups: Personal Finances, Starting and Growing My Business, Find a Better Job, Education for Better Work, and Emergency Preparedness. Contact Nick and Norma King for information: 816-679-1599 or 816-550-5556. Nursery will be provided. Where: Liberty Stake center When: February 17th at 6:00pm
